<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 40px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #2a3d45; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Welcome to Itan 📚</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 30px;">
                <h2 style="color: #333333; margin-top: 0;">Hello <%= @reader.first_name %>,</h2>
                <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  We’re thrilled to have you join <strong>Itan</strong> — the home of African literature.  
                  From timeless classics to modern voices, Itan connects readers like you with stories that inspire, educate, and celebrate African culture.
                </p>

                <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Your account has been confirmed and you can now start exploring books, supporting authors, and enjoying a world of African storytelling.
                </p>

                <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                  <a href="<%= ENV.fetch('READER_FRONTEND_URL', 'https://itan.app') %>" 
                     style="background-color: #2a3d45; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px;">
                    Start Reading
                  </a>
                </div>

                <p style="color: #777777; font-size: 14px;">
                  Welcome aboard,  
                  <br/>
                  — The Itan Team
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #f2f2f2; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">
                © <%= Time.current.year %> Itan. All rights reserved.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
